<ab>Göczen <expan>Schenk<ex>en</ex></expan>, vogt czü
                            <expan>Küngsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her vogt, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                fürbracht Gunther
                                                  <expan>Münczmeist<ex>er</ex></expan> und Hans
                                                Tintner, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie man von in
                                                awsgeb, daz sie <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> czu
                                                  <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> sein süllen.
                                                  <expan>Lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                                                  <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz sie bede
                                                  <expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und auch hie <add>bey
                                                  uns</add> czü <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gesesse<ex>n</ex></expan> sein.
                                                  <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, wo ir in in iren
                                                sachen fürderlich gesein mügt, daz ir das durch
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> tün wöllet, als etc.
                                                Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi
                                                  <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Erhardi.</ab>
</div>
